{"tid":772033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果宋後冇漢人，咁日本人會唔會更加似宋朝前嘅人？","createTime":"2018-08-08T12:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T16:10:58.000Z","uid":98198,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"290067c1af47fc6a7fe71b7c19743140b186ae62","tid":772033,"uid":98198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"宋朝後漢人係真真正正亡國，又被外族入侵<br />\n所以南方人會更加似日本人？"},{"pid":"5df8e367255c10f221d4a8869483833e7b6ff053","tid":772033,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1173bb9398bfdd2aa097130f31f212dd74cb5ddf","tid":772033,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"日本發展出同宋唔一樣嘅文化（以唐為基礎），就算真係想學，要學都係遼同金啦，中原先係正統吖嘛。"},{"pid":"e318ad4c7db04518b1c426a06f2a300ecf6162f3","tid":772033,"uid":165773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T19:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://scholar.harvard.edu/files/elliott/files/critical_han_studies_ch8_elliott.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscholar.harvard.edu%2Ffiles%2Felliott%2Ffiles%2Fcritical_han_studies_ch8_elliott.pdf&d=tuH%2BAwUvH1%2BFk4OrK6UXJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4f045649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://scholar.harvard.edu/files/elliott/files/critical_han_studies_ch8_elliott.pdf</a><br />\n<strong>Initial Moves From Hua to Han第十頁開始</strong><br />\n<br />\n北魏之前居住中原既人就叫漢人 話之你皮膚、頭髮、瞳孔咩顏色<br />\n直程好似美國人咁定義咁 黑白人都可以係美國人<br />\n<br />\n但係北魏開始個定義加入種族成份<br />\n方便統治者趕走某一類敵對種族<br />\n<br />\n所以每個朝定義漢人所包括既種族都唔同<br />\n明朝開國第一次將南人當埋係漢人<br />\n<br />\n基本上漢人一直都係一班大雜炒<br />\n主要居住中原範圍既基因大雜炒"},{"pid":"61901dc5b818ea8a18e778b7822488aec73edd81","tid":772033,"uid":165773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"290067c1af47fc6a7fe71b7c19743140b186ae62","tid":772033,"uid":98198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"宋朝後漢人係真真正正亡國，又被外族入侵<br />\n所以南方人會更加似日本人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n日本人韓國人既基因成份<br />\n更貼近早期「中國」所定義既漢人<br />\n宋朝漢人既基因 係無南人咁滯<br />\n<br />\n因為南人係明朝開國先當埋係漢人"},{"pid":"e563726b0bb71a592004957705b5f5d7ee6d97bf","tid":772033,"uid":150079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"290067c1af47fc6a7fe71b7c19743140b186ae62","tid":772033,"uid":98198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"宋朝後漢人係真真正正亡國，又被外族入侵<br />\n所以南方人會更加似日本人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T19:43:20.000Z","msg":"文化上係，dna唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36c57e5a01445c3d097aff057ea2d8bff62b637","tid":772033,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61901dc5b818ea8a18e778b7822488aec73edd81","tid":772033,"uid":165773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"290067c1af47fc6a7fe71b7c19743140b186ae62","tid":772033,"uid":98198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"宋朝後漢人係真真正正亡國，又被外族入侵<br />\n所以南方人會更加似日本人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n日本人韓國人既基因成份<br />\n更貼近早期「中國」所定義既漢人<br />\n宋朝漢人既基因 係無南人咁滯<br />\n<br />\n因為南人係明朝開國先當埋係漢人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"點解基因係？"},{"pid":"d10894cbe8a2f1a277a73283f84de1d8a360fd6f","tid":772033,"uid":98198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e318ad4c7db04518b1c426a06f2a300ecf6162f3","tid":772033,"uid":165773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T19:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://scholar.harvard.edu/files/elliott/files/critical_han_studies_ch8_elliott.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscholar.harvard.edu%2Ffiles%2Felliott%2Ffiles%2Fcritical_han_studies_ch8_elliott.pdf&d=tuH%2BAwUvH1%2BFk4OrK6UXJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4f045649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://scholar.harvard.edu/file